title: Bwari General Hospital, Bwari, Abuja, FCT
name: Simeon QueenElizabeth Victoria
text:
The hospital tries a lot. It serves a large population, both within Bwari and outside.

The laboratory services are very good.

The X-ray services are fine.

The doctors are doing okay.

They just have to find ways to incorporate cashless services.  All their services are paid for with cash and this sometimes makes getting services quite hard.
